{"tid":826403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(不是軍演) 俄軍機在地中海失踪  俄媒報道疑曾被以色列戰機攻擊","createTime":"2018-09-18T08:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T14:46:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"88793a858d86c1a11f3e55bdd81d5ac8bb3b11c9","tid":826403,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:21:37.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯國防部說，俄軍一架飛機在敘利亞對開的地中海，失去聯絡，並從雷達上消失，正全力搜救。<br />\n<br />\n飛機上有14人，當地星期一晚上11時，在距離敘利亞海岸35公里的地方失聯。當時軍機完成任務，正飛返位於敘利亞西北部城市拉塔基亞的基地。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯有傳媒報道，軍機在拉塔基亞遭遇以色列4架戰機攻擊，之後就從雷達消失。以色列拒絕回應。其他傳媒引述美國國防部匿名官員報道，軍機可能誤被敘利亞防空炮火擊落，敘利亞政府未有評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%84%E8%BB%8D%E6%A9%9F%E5%9C%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%AD%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%B1%E8%81%AF-%E4%BF%84%E5%AA%92%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E7%96%91%E6%9B%BE%E8%A2%AB%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-074954675.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%2581%25AF-%25E4%25BF%2584%25E5%25AA%2592%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2589%25B2%25E5%2588%2597%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A-074954675.html&d=g7k2Ncn0pY6isMlTzy50xTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=17fdf642\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%84%E8%BB%8D%E6%A9%9F%E5%9C%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%AD%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%B1%E8%81%AF-%E4%BF%84%E5%AA%92%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E7%96%91%E6%9B%BE%E8%A2%AB%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-074954675.html</a>"},{"pid":"7eef7df1dcac58b293b9eaa408225f31a793c85b","tid":826403,"uid":4525,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:23:12.000Z","msg":"有藉口了"},{"pid":"ed634b970bdd76ff1a5b936fdf91d811fe91976c","tid":826403,"uid":78873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:24:55.000Z","ms